text: Atrachelus cinereus is a species of assassin bug in the family Reduviidae. It is found in Central America, North America, and South America. ==Subspecies== * Atrachelus cinereus cinereus (Fabricius, 1798) * Atrachelus cinereus wygodzinskyi * Atrachelus cinereus wygoszinskyi Elkins, 1954 ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * * * * * * Category:Reduviidae Category:Insects described in 1798
title: Atrachelus cinereus
